<h1>Timelogger Password Reset</h1>

<p><%= @greeting %></p>

<p>To reset your Timelogger password click the link below:</p>

<%= link_to "Reset password", edit_password_reset_url(id: @user.reset_token,
                                                      email: @user.email) %>

<p>This link will expire in two hours.</p>

<p>
	If you did not request your password to be reset, please ignore this email and
	your password will remain the same.
</p>

<p>Happy logging,</p>
<p>Timelogger Staff</p>

